, then, that women who have no other title are still listed with indicators of their marital status. If relationship status is relevant to achievements warranting honours, then surely we should be given this information for the men too? To do otherwise would surely be illegal discrimination.<br /><strong>Naomi Standen</strong><br /><em>Birmingham</em></p> <p>• The best aphorism in the Guardian of 2014 (Review of the year, G2, 30 December) was by Barney Ronay – he defined God Save the Queen (sung by England fans) as “a plea to an entity that doesn’t exist to preserve one that shouldn’t” (<a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2014/nov/19/lack-imagination-england-fans-chants\" title=\"\">Sport</a>, 20 November). Brilliant.<br /><strong>James Herring</strong><br /><em>Dunbar, East Lothian</em></p> <p>• When I went into the central London branch of my old bank to close the last account, the cashier gave me £3.83, which emptied the account, but said I would need to make an appointment if I wished to close it (<a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/theguardian/2014/dec/30/why-not-use-old-midland-mainline-comet-67p\" title=\"\">Letters</a>, 31 December).<br /><strong>Angela Frampton</strong><br /><em>London</em></p>","internalOctopusCode":"9929880","productionOffice":"UK","newspaperEditionDate":"2015-01-01T00:00:00Z","hasStoryPackage":"false","internalPageCode":"2216744","internalRevision":"11","publication":"The Guardian","trailText":"<strong>Letters:</strong> Sharing our table was a silent and rather sad-looking man. We were told by his companion he was unable to speak so my daughter started signing","allowUgc":"false","headline":"A blizzard, signing and thawed relations","isInappropriateForSponsorship":"false","commentable":"false","firstPublicationDate":"2014-12-31T18:57:50.942Z","secureThumbnail":"https://static-secure.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/12/31/1420052210720/Sign-language-006.jpg","shortUrl":"http://gu.com/p/44gyh","wordcount":"2