matter now being investigated by the Serious Fraud Office.</p> <p>A replacement is being sought for Sir Richard Broadbent, the chairman, while audit committee chairman Ken Hanna and senior independent director Patrick Cescau are also expected to step down next year.</p> <p>Meanwhile, Richard Cousins, the head of giant catering group Compass, and Mikael Ohlsson, a former boss of Ikea, have <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/business/2014/oct/06/tesco-board-retail-experts-ikea-compass\" title=\"\">recently joined the retailer</a>.</p>","internalOctopusCode":"9934886","productionOffice":"UK","newspaperEditionDate":"2015-01-01T00:00:00Z","hasStoryPackage":"true","internalPageCode":"2216814","internalRevision":"7","publication":"The Guardian","trailText":"Overhaul of supermarket’s board continues with replacement of Stuart Chambers, but he will remain on the board","allowUgc":"false","headline":"Tesco head of remuneration committee to step down","isInappropriateForSponsorship":"false","byline":"Sarah Butler","commentable":"false","firstPublicationDate":"2014-12-31T18:08:38.109Z","secureThumbnail":"https://static-secure.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/12/31/1420049265715/Tesco-006.jpg","shortUrl":"http://gu.com/p/44gz6","wordcount":"151","shouldHideAdverts":"false","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/12/31/1420049265715/Tesco-006.jpg","isPremoderated":"false","internalComposerCode":"54a43a90e4b084424a7b2ea3","newspaperPageNumber":"28","internalStoryPackageCode":"83843","commentCloseDate":"2015-01-03T18:08:39Z","standfirst":"Overhaul of supermarket’s board continues with replacement of Stuart Chambers, but he will remain on the board","linkText":"Tesco head of remuneration committee to step down","showInRelatedContent":"true","lastModified":"2015-01-02T15:21:42.000Z","internalContentCode":"454076512"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/business/2014/dec/31/tesco-head-remuneration-committee-step-down","apiUrl":"ht